{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01FS86dQLLs4NBEZ8SkhVFce","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013G3QGF3DSvPPimwXRiAcbP","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- `patches/infra/` directory doesn't exist yet — first file created there","new_string":"- `patches/infra/` directory doesn't exist yet — first file created there\n\n### 4-1-dockerfile-rules-validation — dev-story (2026-03-21T05:22Z)\n\n- **Branch coverage at 87.5%** — The `line !== undefined` conditional in `dfGap()` helper has one branch not fully covered. Cosmetic; both paths exercised indirectly.\n- **Verification tools check has potential false positives** — Regex checks for tool names anywhere in apt-get/apk lines. Matches story's stated approach: \"False positives are acceptable.\"\n- **Dual file reads in checkInfrastructure** — Dockerfile read once for precondition checks, then again by `validateDockerfile()`. Intentional for backward-compatible error messages but redundant."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1180,"cache_read_input_tokens":44258,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1180},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ef2f2ce5-c013-4ad4-b6dd-a80c40f8ca85","uuid":"016074a6-c902-44fa-9756-30ef963aee5e"}
